strings: <voice_0x0100109E><se_def>chondromas: Hello, Felix's teacher is not here!
<voice_0x0100109F><se_def>chondromas: ...I'm sorry!; Is Professor Felix asking for help?
<voice_0x010010A0><se_def>chondromas: If he takes you on one of his big trains, he'll think you're wearing cat pajamas!
<voice_0x010010A1><se_def>chondromas: Nice guy! I have the right to let you in!
<voice_0x010010A2><se_def>chondromas: You were a cute cat. I listened!
<voice_0x010010A4><se_def>chondromas: That's true? Let me take care of it! Don't be ashamed of the cat!
<voice_0x010010A5><se_def>chondromas: Be brave and everything will be okay!
<voice_0x010010A6><se_def>chondromas: Yes it is, no effect, pain gone!
<voice_0x010010A8><se_def>chondromas: I want to talk about the basics of sword fighting.
<voice_0x010010A9><se_def>chondromas: Riding a cat is faster than walking...
<voice_0x010010AA><se_def>chondromas: But you still can't do that. You can get to the same place faster. Some people misunderstand this, so I want to clarify.
<voice_0x010010AB><se_def>chondromas: If you accidentally lost a cat on the street. Contact us I want to rent as many cats as possible.
<voice_0x010010AC><se_def>chondromas: I realized it! ready to play
